{"tid":2327631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Chickeeduck天后開舖賣「香港人」燙章迷你民女像 供同路人擺賣籲港人勿放棄","createTime":"2020-12-16T08:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T08:24:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ce9d3a75e7aea5c75f75c2eae6028d0d8dda86","tid":2327631,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rCQ0hgPYrAfK9IwKiuuZST3r7yo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F2CZEJ7DFBA7DPKRFAYST45ASE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrCQ0hgPYrAfK9IwKiuuZST3r7yo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF2CZEJ7DFBA7DPKRFAYST45ASE.png&h=4d1b2e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連鎖童裝品牌Chickeeduck早前在多間分店擺放「民主女神像」後遭接連打壓，包括被商場要求將民女像移除。Chickeeduck本月在天后興發街開設藝術生活百貨店，除了售賣品牌T-shirt外，更有多款與社會運動相關的產品出售，包括「香港人」燙章、迷你版民女像及「手足同行玻璃杯」等。集團行政總裁周小龍稱，天后屬「希望店」，除了提供平台予本地藝術家或同路人擺賣相關產品外，亦希望透過該店提醒香港人希望仍在，不要放棄，他將與同路人繼續「齊上齊落，撐到最後」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/3Q6TCI64P5FYHLJIK2QNAE5WF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2F3Q6TCI64P5FYHLJIK2QNAE5WF4%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=c904da33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2F3Q6TCI64P5FYHLJIK2QNAE5WF4%2F&h=ce3f2a03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/3Q6TCI64P5FYHLJIK2QNAE5WF4/</a>"},{"pid":"f9c2677dfa2b0dc8f4158bd703ea3443c191fac8","tid":2327631,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"又迫害肛榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\